      "text": [
        " : «إِذَا ضَلَلْتَ عَنِ اَلطَّرِيقِ فَنَادِ: يَا صَالِحُ أَوْ يَا أَبَا صَالِحٍ أَرْشِدُونَا إِلَى اَلطَّرِيقِ يَرْحَمُكُمُ اَللَّهُ »."
      ],
      "translations": {
        "en.bab-ul-qaim-publications": [
          "Hadith.2506 - Ali ibn Abi Hamzah narrated from Abu Basir, from Abu Abdullah (as), who said:\n\"If you lose your way, call out: 'O Righteous One! O Abu Salih! Guide us to the path, may Allah (swt) have mercy on you.'\""
        ]
      }
